name: Signpost 1
Dialogue: SILPH's latest product! Release to be determined...

name: Signpost 2
Dialogue:
TRAINER TIPS
New GREAT BALL offers improved capture rates. Try it on those
hard-to-catch POKEMON.

name: Signpost 3
Dialogue:
TRAINER TIPS
FULL HEAL cures all ailments like sleep and burns. It costs a bit
more, but it's more convenient.
What do you want? Get lost!
BOSS said he'll take this town!
Get out of the way!
SAFFRON belongs to TEAM ROCKET!
Ow! Watch where you're walking!
Being evil makes me feel so alive!
With SILPH under control, we can exploit POKEMON around the world!

name: Center 1
Dialogue: It would be great if the ELITE FOUR came and stomped TEAM ROCKET!

name: Center 2
Dialogue: POKEMON growth rates differ from specie [sic] to specie [sic].

name: Center 3
Dialogue: SILPH CO. is very famous. That's why it attracted TEAM ROCKET!

name: Mart 4
Dialogue: REVIVE is costly, but it revives fainted POKEMON!

name: Mart 5
Dialogue:
MAX REPEL lasts longer than SUPER REPEL for keeping weaker POKEMON
away!

name: Mr.Psychic
Dialogue: ...Wait! Don't say a word! You wanted this!
Where do you plan to put this?
TM29 is PSYCHIC! It can lower the target's SPECIAL abilities.

name: Trainer 1 dojo
Dialogue: Hoohah! You're trespassing in our FIGHTING DOJO!

name: Trainer 1 dojo after
Dialogue: The prime fighters across the land train here.

name: Trainer 2 dojo
Dialogue: I hear you're good! Show me!

name: Trainer 2 dojo after
Dialogue: Our Master is a pro fighter!

name: Trainer 3 dojo
Dialogue: Nothing tough frightens me! I break boulders for training!

name: Trainer 3 dojo after
Dialogue: The only thing that frightens us is psychic power!

name: Trainer 4 dojo
Dialogue: Hoargh! Take your shoes off!

name: Trainer 4 dojo after
Dialogue:
You wait 'til you see our Master! I'm a small fry compared
to him!

name: Trainer 5 dojo
Dialogue:
Grunt! I am the KARATE MASTER! I am the LEADER here!
You wish to challenge us? Expect no mercy! Fwaaa!

name: Trainer 5 dojo after
Dialogue:
Indeed, I have lost! But, I beseech you, do not take our emblem
as your trophy! In return, I will give you a prized fighting
POKEMON! Choose wichever one you like!

name: Trainer 5 given tm
Dialogue: Ho! Stay and train at Karate with us!

name: Silph Co Guard
Dialogue: I'm a security guard. Suspicious kids I don't allow in!

name: Silph Co Guard after
Dialogue: ...Snore...
Hah! He's taking a snooze!

name: Trainer 1 Silph Co
Dialogue: Hey kid! What are you doing here?

name: Trainer 1 Silph Co after
Dialogue: SILPH CO. will be merged with TEAM ROCKET!

name: Trainer 2 Silph Co
Dialogue: It's off limits here! Go home!

name: Trainer 2 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Can you solve the maze in here?

name: Trainer 3 Silph Co
Dialogue: No kids are allowed in here!

name: Trainer 3 Silph Co after
Dialogue:
Diamond shaped tiles are teleport blocks! They're hi-tech
transporters!

name: Trainer 4 Silph Co
Dialogue: Help! I'm a SILPH employee.

name: Trainer 4 Silph Co after
Dialogue: I work for both SILPH and TEAM ROCKET!

name: Silph Co 1
Dialogue:
Eeek! No! Stop! Help! Oh, you're not with TEAM ROCKET. I thought...
I'm sorry. Here, please take this!
You don't have any room for this.

TM36 is SELFDESTRUCT! It's powerful, but the POKEMON that uses it
faints! Be careful.

name: Silph Co 1 after
Dialogue: Be careful.

name: Trainer 5 Silph Co
Dialogue: Quit messing with us, kid!

name: Trainer 5 Silph Co after
Dialogue: A hint? You can open doors with a CARD KEY!

name: Trainer 6 Silph Co
Dialogue: I support TEAM ROCKET more than I support SILPH!

name: Trainer 6 Silph Co after
Dialogue:
Humph... TEAM ROCKET said that if I helped them, they'd let me
study POKEMON!

name: Silph Co 2
Dialogue: I work for SILPH. What should I do?

name: Trainer 7 Silph Co
Dialogue: Intruder spotted!

name: Trainer 7 Silph Co after
Dialogue: I better tell the BOSS on 11F!

name: Trainer 8 Silph Co
Dialogue: TEAM ROCKET has taken command of SILPH CO.!

name: Trainer 8 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Fwahahaha! My BOSS has been after this place!

name: Trainer 9 Silph Co
Dialogue: My POKEMON are my loyal soldiers!

name: Trainer 9 Silph Co after
Dialogue: The doors are electronically locked! A CARD KEY opens them!

name: Silph Co 3
Dialogue: Sssh! Can't you see I'm hiding?

name: Paper 1
Dialogue:
It's a POKEMON REPORT! 4 POKEMON evolve only when traded by
link-cable.

name: Paper 2
Dialogue:
It's a POKEMON REPORT! Over 160 POKEMON techniques have been
confirmed.

name: Paper 3
Dialogue:
It's a POKEMON REPORT! POKEMON LAB created PORYGON, the first
virtual reality POKEMON.

name: Trainer 10 Silph Co
Dialogue: Show TEAM ROCKET a little respect!

name: Trainer 10 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Which reminds me. KOFFING evolves into WEEZING!

name: Trainer 11 Silph Co
Dialogue: Whaaat? There shouldn't be any children here?

name: Trainer 11 Silph Co after
Dialogue: You're only on 5F. It's a long way to my BOSS!

name: Trainer 12 Silph Co
Dialogue: We study POKE BALL technology on this floor!

name: Trainer 12 Silph Co after
Dialogue: We worked on the ultimate POKE BALL which would catch anything!

name: Trainer 13 Silph Co
Dialogue: I heard a kid was wandering around.

name: Trainer 13 Silph Co after
Dialogue: It's not smart to pick a fight with TEAM ROCKET!

name: Silph Co 4
Dialogue: TEAM ROCKET is in an uproar over some intruder. That's you right?

name: Trainer 14 Silph Co
Dialogue: I am one of the 4 ROCKET BROTHERS!

name: Trainer 14 Silph Co after
Dialogue: No matter! My brothers will avenge me!

name: Trainer 15 Silph Co
Dialogue: You dare betray TEAM ROCKET?

name: Trainer 15 Silph Co after
Dialogue: If you stand for justice, you betray evil!

name: Trainer 16 Silph Co
Dialogue:
That rotten PRESIDENT! He shouldn't have sent me to the TIKSI
BRANCH!

name: Trainer 16 Silph Co after
Dialogue: TIKSI BRANCH? It's in Russian no man's land!

name: Silph Co 5
Dialogue: Oh dear, oh dear. Help me please!

name: Silph Co 6
Dialogue: Look at him! He's such a coward!

name: Silph Co 7
Dialogue: They must have targeted SILPH for our POKEMON products.

name: Silph Co 8
Dialogue: The ROCKETs came and took over the building!

name: Silph Co 9
Dialogue: TEAM ROCKET is trying to conquer the world with POKEMON!

name: Trainer 17 Silph Co
Dialogue: I am one of the 4 ROCKET BROTHERS!

name: Trainer 17 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Doesn't matter. My brothers will repay the favor!

name: Trainer 18 Silph Co
Dialogue: A child intruder! That must be you!

name: Trainer 18 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Go on home before my BOSS gets ticked off!

name: Trainer 19 Silph Co
Dialogue: Oh ho! I smell a little rat!

name: Trainer 19 Silph Co after
Dialogue: You won't find my boss by just scurrying around!

name: Trainer 20 Silph Co
Dialogue: Heheh! You mistook me for a SILPH worker?

name: Trainer 20 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Despite your age, you are a skilled trainer!

name: Silph Co 10
Dialogue: You! It's really dangerous here! You came to save me? You can't!

name: Silph Co 11
Dialogue: It would be bad if TEAM ROCKET took over SILPH or our POKEMON!

name: Silph Co 12
Dialogue: TEAM ROCKET was after the MASTER BALL which will catch any POKEMON!

name: Trainer 21 Silph Co
Dialogue: That's as far as you'll go!

name: Trainer 21 Silph Co after
Dialogue: If you don't turn back, I'll call for backup!

name: Trainer 22 Silph Co
Dialogue: I am one of the 4 ROCKET BROTHERS!

name: Trainer 22 Silph Co after
Dialogue: I'll leave you up to my brothers!

name: Trainer 23 Silph Co
Dialogue: You're causing us problems!

name: Trainer 23 Silph Co after
Dialogue: So, what do you think of SILPH BUILDING's maze?

name: Silph Co 13
Dialogue: I wonder if SILPH is finished...

name: Trainer 24 Silph Co
Dialogue: Your POKEMON have weak points! I can nail them!

name: Trainer 24 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Exploiting weak spots does work! Think about element types!

name: Trainer 25 Silph Co
Dialogue: I am one of the 4 ROCKET BROTHERS!

name: Trainer 25 Silph Co after
Dialogue: My brothers will avenge me!

name: Trainer 26 Silph Co
Dialogue: Your POKEMON seem to adore you, kid!

name: Trainer 26 Silph Co after
Dialogue: If I had started as a trainer at your age...

name: Silph Co 14
Dialogue: You look tired! You should take a quick nap! Don't give up!

name: Trainer 27 Silph Co
Dialogue: Enough of your silly games!

name: Trainer 27 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Are you satisfied with beating me? Then go on home!

name: Trainer 28 Silph Co
Dialogue: Welcome to the 10F! So good of you to join me!

name: Trainer 28 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Nice try, but the boardroom is up one more floor!

name: Silph Co 15
Dialogue: Waaaaa! I'm scared!

name: Trainer 29 Silph Co
Dialogue: Halt! Do you have an appointment with my BOSS?

name: Trainer 29 Silph Co after
Dialogue: Watch your step, my BOSS likes his POKEMON tough!

name: Rival_Fight
Dialogue:
What kept you Player? Hahaha! I thought you'd turn up if I waited
here! I guess TEAM ROCKET slowed you down! Not that I care!
I saw you in SAFFRON, so I decided to see if you got better!

name: Rival_Fight after
Dialogue:
Well, RED! I'm moving on up and ahead! By checking my POKEDEX,
I'm starting to see what's strong and how they evolve! I'm going
to the POKEMON LEAGUE to boot out the ELITE FOUR! I'll become
the world's most powerful trainer! RED, well good luck to you!
Don't sweat it! Smell ya!

name: Silph Co 16
Dialogue:
Oh! Hi! You're not a ROCKET! You came to save us? Why, thank you!
I want you to have this POKEMON for saving us.

It's LAPRAS. It's very intelligent. We kept it in our lab, but it
will be much better off with you! I think you will be a good trainer
for LAPRAS! It's a good swimmer. It'll give you a lift!

name: Silph Co 16 after
Dialogue: TEAM ROCKET's BOSS went to the boardroom! Is our PRESIDENT OK?

name: Trainer 31 Silph Co
Dialogue: Stop right there! Don't you move!

name: Trainer 31 Silph Co after
Dialogue: So, you want to see my BOSS?

name: Giovanni
Dialogue:
Ah Player! So we meet again! The PRESIDENT and I are discussing
a vital business proposition. Keep your nose out of grown-up
matters... Or, experience a world of pain!

name: Giovanni after
Dialogue:
Blast it all! You ruined our plans for SILPH! But, TEAM ROCKET
will never fall! RED! Never forget that all POKEMON exist for
TEAM ROCKET! I must go, but I shall return!

name: Secretary
Dialogue: Thank you for rescuing all of us! We admire your courage.

name: President
Dialogue:
Thank you for saving SILPH! I will never forget you saved us in our
moment of peril! I have to thank you in some way! Because I am rich,
I can give you anything! Here, maybe this will do!
You have no room for this.

You can't buy that anywhere! It's our secret prototype MASTER BALL!
It will catch any POKEMON without fail! You should be quiet about
using it, though.

name: 1 after
Dialogue: I saw ROCKET BOSS escaping SILPH's building.

name: 2 after
Dialogue:
I flew here on my PIDGEOT when I read about SILPH. It's already
over? I missed the media action.

name: 3 after
Dialogue: Yeah! TEAM ROCKET is gone! It's safe to go out again!

name: 4 after
Dialogue: People should be flocking back to SAFFRON now.

name: 5 after
Dialogue: You beat TEAM ROCKET all alone? That's amazing!

name: Center 1 after
Dialogue: TEAM ROCKET took off! We can go out safely again! That's great!

name: Center 2 after
Dialogue: POKEMON growth rates differ from specie [sic] to specie [sic].

name: Center 3 after
Dialogue: SILPH CO. is very famous. That's why it attracted TEAM ROCKET!

name: Mart 4 after
Dialogue: REVIVE is costly, but it revives fainted POKEMON!

name: Mart 5 after
Dialogue:
MAX REPEL lasts longer than SUPER REPEL for keeping weaker POKEMON
away!

name: Letter
Dialogue:
I was given a PP UP as a gift. It's used for increasing the PP
of techniques!

name: 6 after
Dialogue: Thank you for writing. I hope to see you soon!

name: 7 after
Dialogue: The COPYCAT is cute! I'm getting her a POKE DOLL!

name: Pidgey
Dialogue: Kurukkoo!

name: Chansey
Dialogue: Chaan! Sii!

My daughter likes to mimic people. Her mimicry has earned her the
nickname COPYCAT around here!
My daughter is so self-centered. She only has a few friends.

name: Copycat
Dialogue:
Player: Hi! Do you like POKEMON?
Uh no, I just asked you.
Huh? You're strange!
Copycat: Hmm? Quit mimicking? But, that's my favorite hobby!
Copycat: Oh wow! A POKE DOLL! For me? Thank you! You can have this, then!
Don't you want this?
TM31 contains my favorite, MIMIC! Use it on a good POKEMON!

name: Copycat after
Dialogue:
Player: Hi! Thanks for TM31!
Pardon?
Is it that fun to mimic my every move?
Copycat: You bet! It's a scream!

name: Building 1
Dialogue:
TM36 is SELFDESTRUCT! It's powerful, but the POKEMON that uses it
faints! Be careful.

name: Building 2
Dialogue: Player! You and your POKEMON saved us!

name: Building 3
Dialogue: Huh? TEAM ROCKET is gone?

name: Building 4
Dialogue: TEAM ROCKET took off! You're our hero! Thank you!

name: Building 5
Dialogue: We got engaged! Heheh!

name: Building 6
Dialogue: I feel so sorry for him, I have to marry him!

name: Building 7
Dialogue: Come work for SILPH when you get older!

name: Building 8
Dialogue: Well, better get back to work!

name: Building 9
Dialogue: TEAM ROCKET ran because of you!

name: Building 10
Dialogue: Safe at last! Oh thank you!

name: Building 11
Dialogue: Wow! You chased off TEAM ROCKET all by yourself?

name: Building 12
Dialogue: We canceled the MASTER BALL project because of TEAM ROCKET.

name: Building 13
Dialogue: Thanks for saving us!

name: Building 14
Dialogue: Thank you so much!

name: Building 15
Dialogue: Please keep quiet about my crying!

name: Building 16
Dialogue: Saved at last! Thank you!

name: Building 17
Dialogue: Welcome! The PRESIDENT is in the boardroom on 11F!

name: Gym Signpost
Dialogue:
SAFFRON CITY POKEMON GYM
LEADER: SABRINA
The Master of Psychic POKEMON!

name: Plaque
Dialogue: WINNING TRAINERS: Rival

name: Gym 1
Dialogue:
Yo! Champ in making! SABRINA's POKEMON use psychic power instead of
force! Fighting POKEMON are weak against psychic POKEMON! They get
creamed before they can even aim a punch!

name: Gym 1 after
Dialogue: Psychic power, huh? If I had that, I'd make a bundle at the slots!

name: Trainer 1 Gym
Dialogue:
SABRINA is young, but she's also our LEADER! You won't reach her
easily!

name: Trainer 1 Gym after
Dialogue:
There used to be 2 POKEMON GYMs in SAFFRON. The FIGHTING DOJO
next door lost its GYM status when we went and creamed them!

name: Trainer 2 Gym
Dialogue: You know that power alone isn't enough!

name: Trainer 2 Gym after
Dialogue: SABRINA just wiped out the KARATE MASTER next door!

name: Trainer 3 Gym
Dialogue: Does our unseen power scare you?

name: Trainer 3 Gym after
Dialogue: Psychic POKEMON fear only ghosts and bugs!

name: Trainer 4 Gym
Dialogue: SABRINA is younger than I, but I respect her!

name: Trainer 4 Gym after
Dialogue:
In a battle of equals, the one with the stronger will wins!
If you wish to beat SABRINA, focus on winning!

name: Trainer 5 Gym
Dialogue:
SAFFRON POKEMON GYM is famous for its psychics! You want to see
SABRINA! I can tell!

name: Trainer 5 Gym after
Dialogue: That's right! I used telepathy to read your mind!

name: Trainer 6 Gym
Dialogue:
POKEMON take on the appearance of their trainers. Your POKEMON
must be tough, then!

name: Trainer 6 Gym after
Dialogue: I must teach better techniques to my POKEMON!

name: Trainer 7 Gym
Dialogue: You and I, our POKEMON shall fight!

name: Trainer 7 Gym after
Dialogue: I knew that this was going to take place.

name: Sabrina
Dialogue:
I had a vision of your arrival! I have had psychic powers since I
was a child. I first learned to bend spoons with my mind.
 I dislike fighting, but if you wish, I will show you my powers!

name: Sabrina after
Dialogue: Everyone has psychic power! People just don't realize it!
